      "content": "@Bombfuse You can't order a single chip in wafer.space ... you get 1000 ... there is no way to manufacture a _single_ custom chip at any reasonable price.\n\nWhat TT does is take one slot of wafer.space and divide it into ~150 tiles. So obviously the area each tile gets is much smaller but then the cost is also divided ...",
